subject: [Info] two apparent typos in section 9 of mint.com terms
text:

"These alerts allow you to choose alert messages for your accounts."
These alerts -> These settings

"If your email address or your mobile deviceâ€™s email address changes, you are responsible for informing us of that change."
mobile device's email address -> mobile device's phone number
